  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 300 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Heat the vegetable broth in a large pot over medium heat until simmering.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and potato to the pot and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the fish fillet to the pot and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the tomato paste, dried thyme, and black pepper.",
    "Transfer the pot to the preheated oven and braise for 20 minutes.",
    "Remove the pot from the oven and stir in the oat milk.",
    "Serve the stew hot, topped with crushed whole wheat crackers for a crumbly texture, on a talavera plate."
